18
00:02:45,630 --> 00:02:46,270
I heard

19
00:02:46,390 --> 00:02:47,590
the rouge made from it

20
00:02:47,750 --> 00:02:49,150
is only for the Second Lady.

21
00:02:53,020 --> 00:02:53,510
Your Highness.

22
00:03:05,430 --> 00:03:05,950
Stop.

23
00:03:07,230 --> 00:03:07,790
You there,

24
