27
00:03:15,550 --> 00:03:16,430
Thank you, Prince Yi.

28
00:03:21,310 --> 00:03:22,910
If you want to see me, just say so.

29
00:03:23,430 --> 00:03:25,110
Don't use the excuse of giving plants.

30
00:03:25,829 --> 00:03:27,310
If you don't have them,

31
