56
00:05:06,910 --> 00:05:07,590
So...

57
00:05:07,590 --> 00:05:08,430
The morning dews on the flowers
 are like makeup...

58
00:05:08,430 --> 00:05:10,110
Hearing the person you like recite a poem

59
00:05:10,350 --> 00:05:11,670
feels so sweet.

60
